name: Large Starburst Earrings
description: These are just like the smaller version, except they measure closer to 3.5" long and they have a french hook instead of a post. They are awesome!

name: Small Starburst Earrings
description: These silver beauties measure approximately 2.5" and look amazing with shorter haircuts. They are polished to a bright finish.

name: Chevron Oval Earrings
description: I love this design. It is simple, but beautiful and unique. These earrings measure approximately 3.5" long and have a bright silver polish.

name: Rainbow Oval Hoops
description: Super delicate and lightweight, but strong due to the relentless hammering. These are statement earrings, measuring approximately 3.5".

name: Large Simple Oval Earrings
description: You will wear these everyday. They are like the simple hoop earring that everyone loves, just a new shape. They are made from very delicate sterling silver, but hand forged for extreme strength. They are lightweight and are polished to a bright silver. These are approximately 3.5" long.

name: Small Simple Oval Earring
description: You will wear these everyday. They are like the simple hoop earring that everyone loves, just a new shape. They are made from very delicate sterling silver, but hand forged for extreme strength. They are lightweight and are polished to a bright silver. They measure approximately 2.5" long.

name: Meteor Necklace
description: I love this piece. It is beautiful in the way that the hoop is this hard forged hunk of metal, but it is balanced with the dangling delicacy of the chain. It catches the light beautifully and really dresses up any outfit. It measures approximately 18".

name: Triple Weights Necklace
description: Hand forged sterling silver hoops hanging from a sterling venetian box chain. Approx. 18" long. Antiqued patina finish.

name: Circle Weight Necklace
description: A hand forged sterling silver hoop dangling from a beautiful venetian box chain at approx. 18". Simple and classic. Antique patina finish.

name: Paisley Stud Earrings
description: I love this shape and I think it is under appreciated. Hence these simple stud earrings, hand forged sterling with an antiqued patina finish.

name: Teardrop Stud Earring
description: Hand forged sterling silver with an antiqued patina finish.

name: Circle Stud Earrings
description: Simple little circle studs, perfect for everyday. Forged sterling silver with an antiqued patina finish.

name: Weights Necklace
description: This necklace is interesting in that there is no clasp. The heavy bars of silver slip through the textured hoops and the weight of them holds the necklace in place. My best selling necklace yet.

name: Teardrop Necklace
description: This piece moves beautifully due to the balanced weight. All sterling silver components are forged by hand and finished with a patina to add an antiqued look. This is such an original piece, it is certainly one of my favorites to wear. The clasp is worn to the side to accentuate the beauty of that connection.

name: Weights Earring
description: I love these heavily hammered stick earrings. They seem so understated, but they look great on. Definitely one of my biggest sellers.

name: Teardrop Earrings
description: Heavily hammered sterling silver earrings. Simple and beautiful.

name: Badass Bangle Set
description: This is a mixed set of sterling silver bangles. There are ten super thin and delicate bangles, three heavy gauged bangles with lots of texturing on the finish and one beaded bangle. They all have a patina added to enhance the texturing. They are awesome and will definitely become an everyday accessory.

name: Dog Tag Necklace
description:
I love the little connections I have made with people through making these necklaces. There is something about the custom work that gives me a little peak inside the lives of my customers, which so rarely happens. I have made these necklaces for pet lovers, baby shower gifts, anniversaries, self empowerment reminders, and countless mothers. They are small so they remain personal, but still make a beautiful statement worn with other jewelry or on their own. 

The tags are sterling silver and come on a delicate 18" sterling silver chain. They are each approximately 1/4" wide and as long as they need to be to accommodate the stamping. I have numbers and capitol letters. Please limit the number of characters per tag to 10.

To order, email me with the words/numbers you would like stamped on each tag and if you would prefer a bright silver polish finish (#1 picture) or an antiqued patina finish (#2 picture). I will then email you a PayPal invoice and get to work making your personalized necklace!

(You can order additional tags on the necklace, they are $12 each.)

name: Lovelight Necklace
description: This is one of those pieces that I didn't have any plan for, and as it unfolded I couldn't believe what a lovely form occurred. I used brass to build the pendant as well as the clasp. The chain is made up of a brown and a green corded leather. It is approximately 20" long.

name: Beach Bum Necklace
description: You want a long necklace? You got it. This awesome piece measures almost 40" long. I used brass to build the chain elements and a gorgeous leather for the chain. You can wear it with the larger chain in front or at the nape of your neck, whichever you prefer. You can also double it up with both of the chains in front and it looks stunning. I think it looks best with nothing on but a bathing suit and shades...but that is just me.

name: Nag Champa Chime Earrings
description: Making these earrings made me feel transported to yurt in the desert with hand woven afghans on the floor and nag champa smoke filling the room. I mean this in a good way. It was awesome. I wanna go back. Alas, I must stay here for now, so I will have to just keep creating these earrings to take me back for visits in my mind. Sterling silver was forged and soldered and finished with a patina and some darling turquoise and lapis beads to make these earrings. They measure approx. 2" long.

name: Amoeba Moves West Earrings
description: Hands down, my favorite earrings to date. They are beautiful off and even more beautiful on. These partial hoops are so badass, I can't even believe I made them. They are super light weight, but they have a toughness to them that makes me feel really sexy when I wear them. Sexy, in a mean, hot, bartender at the dive bar kinda way. Do you know what I mean? I guess you just have to wear them to get it, but believe me when I tell you that they look gooooooooood. They have a patina and measure approx. 1.5" long.

name: Floret Hoop Earrings
description: These earrings are a fun, flirty version of a simple hoop. They remind me of a flower basket in a way, but because they rotate around they actually create really interesting designs that I wasn't expecting when I was making them. They are sterling with a slight patina and they are approx. 1.75" in diameter.

name: Weaving Cane Earrings
description: I really love these simple oval hoops. The line work in the interior reminds me of the basket weaving that my next door neighbor used to do when I was a child. I never did learn that craft, but what a wonderful skill to have. These earrings are sterling with a slight patina and measure approx. 1.75" long

name: Light as a Feather Earrings
description: Similar to the necklace, these earrings are simple, yet elegant. They are sterling silver with a slight patina finish. They measure approx. 2" long

name: Wrinkle Rings
description: These rings are so cute and they look awesome stacked together. The negative space that the wrinkles create against your finger looks really beautiful. They are polished silver and come in a variety of sizes. They are sold individually, but I highly recommend wearing at least three together. Don't be fooled by how delicate and thin they are. Just like the wrinkle bracelets, they have been beaten to death and are much stronger than they look!

name: Smoke Rings Bracelet
description: Clearly, there was a lot of sweat that went into making this bracelet. Partially because of how many components there where to forge and solder, but also because my studio doesn't have AC and we are getting into 100 degree weather here in Austin! I adore this bracelet nonetheless. It was so fun to make and it looks awesome on. It has a darker patina which helps bring out some of the forging marks from the hammer. It looks great paired with polished sterling bangles too or just by itself. It also has a lovely hand forged clasp, all sterling silver.

name: What a Little Moonlight Can Do
description: My obsession with turquoise and sterling silver will never end. Especially when you add a little patina to the silver to give it an aged quality, it looks incredible paired with the luscious hues of turquoise.Each sterling element on this necklace was sawed out by hand, formed and textured before it was "antiqued" with patina. The clasp detail might be my favorite part. This is a shorter necklace than most, measuring approx. 20" long.

name: This Bird Can Fly Necklace
description: Simple, graceful, elegant and definitely one of a kind. This piece is really gorgeous, with a slight antique quality to it. Dress up your day wear or add some refinement to evening wear. There is a subtle bead detailing at the nape of the neck which adds a flirtatious element to this otherwise very mature and confident piece. This necklace measures approx. 32" long.

name: Give Me a Beat Necklace
description: I love Lapis. It has such a richness to it, the color is unmistakable. This stone is so strong it really speaks for itself. So when trying to design a necklace for it, I knew it needed powerful elements that could support the stone, but not overwhelm it. I love the components I came up with and especially the way that the are repeating patterns in varying sizes. This necklace is not for the subtle look, it is proud and beautiful and makes me wanna rock! It measures approx. 32" long.

name: Evening Blossom Necklace
description: This is one of the few shorter necklaces I have made. It has a hand forged clasp, beautiful stones and interlocking petal shaped sterling silver elements. This piece is slightly more versatile than the others in that it has a more refined quality to it and a brighter polished finish. It measures approx. 20" long.

name: Triple Rainbow Necklace
description: You wont believe me, but I have seen a triple rainbow. What does it all mean? I don't know, but I like it. This necklace is awesome and colorful and flirty and youthful and I love it. Looks great against a white button down or over your favorite swimsuit. Looks great with just about anything but a sweatsuit. But then again, if you are wearing a sweatsuit, more power to ya and I say go ahead and pair it with this necklace. It measures approx. 30" long.

name: Night Swim Necklace
description: Oh night swim, I will never outgrow you. Throw a light cotton shirt over a bikini and don't worry about taking your jewelry off. Dive in the cool water and let your body float to the top while you gaze up at the stars. With a super soft leather chord, the sterling silver hoops, turquoise and lapis on this necklace glimmer and spin against the waves. This go-to favorite measures approx. 29" long.

name: Flowers In Her Hair
description: Floral imagery is such an easy way to express beauty, femininity, sweetness and warmth. I can't get enough of them myself. This is very simple line work using flower forms. I adore the antique finish of the sterling in conjunction with the pink and yellowed stones. It has a very vintage quality to it that will always be in style. It measures approx. 29" long.

name: Amoeba Moves West Necklace
description: I always think of turquoise when I think of the west. Probably because most of my mothers jewelry came from her time living in Flagstaff, Arizona, and all of it had turquoise. I can still remember trying on all of her rings at once and admiring my hands swimming in a sea of silver and the gorgeous green/blue stone. This necklace reminds me of those rings in that it is simple, but striking. The sterling components were painstakingly soldered together one at a time, but I think it was worth it. This piece measures approx. 34" long.

name: TAMBOURINE MAN NECKLACE
description: This is by far one of my favorite pieces. It reminds me so much of the jewelry my mother used to hold onto from her youth. The colors have a very desert feel to me, rich browns, oranges and greens. That paired with the dark patina on the silver elements makes an awesome color combination. The silver components are all cut by hand, formed and textured before I add the patina. A lot of love went into making this piece. This necklace measures approx. 32" long and looks great with anything.

name: Hoop Ring
description: These little hoop rings are so cute! They are made of sterling silver and forged into shape. They have a soft square shaped body which fits the finger really comfortably. They look great on any finger, but my favorite is the thumb!

name: Wrinkled Bangles
description: Who doesn't love a big stack of bangles? I know I do. This is a set of five super delicate bangles. Don't worry about them being fragile though, I have beat them to death with my hammer so you can't hurt them! They have a nice high polish and with the crinkle profile, they catch the light beautifully. They measure about 7.75 inches around. They are light, elegant and look awesome when stacked with other bracelets.

name: Light as a Feather Necklace
description: I love the detail of this piece. The sterling silver components actually rest on the nape of the neck, which creates a beautiful element of surprise. I used a lovely ivory tear shaped agate as well as pale pink and green beads to soften the antiqued finish of the sterling silver. This necklace measures approximately 36 inches.

name: Florets Necklace
description: The most delicate and feminine of the the necklaces was inspired by one of my most lovely friends. All of the florets are hand forged from sterling silver and are connected to a delicate sterling chain. It is 32" long, flowing down the neck and no matter how it moves it looks beautiful in the light. Just like she does.

name: SWEET AND SALTY NECKLACE
description: Floral designs hand forged and soldered from sterling silver were the beginning elements of this design. Using pale pink and muddled violet, and light brown stones helped rough up the sweetness of the flower petals. This necklace measures approximately 28" long on a sterling silver chain.

name: ON THE ROAD AGAIN NECKLACE
description: This necklace was made while listening to Fleetwood Mac and daydreaming about hitting the road driving west with nothing but a camp stove, a blanket and some trust worthy boots. It measures 32" long, so it can be worn long or doubled up around the neck. The delicate sterling silver chain hosts multiple hand forged sterling interlocking hoops and hand picked stones.
